    "description": {
      "chat": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>You have used your unique biology to bud off a biological drone you can more easily integrate with.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites</strong>: Drone class feature, adaptation or early stage adaptation species trait.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Benefit</strong>: Your drone has living components. You can use Medicine instead of Engineering to repair it, and your drone naturally heals to full Hit Points when you rest for 8 hours. A drone modified in this way is considered an aberration rather than a construct for the purpose of spells and effects targeting it. In addition, Life Science and Medicine become class skills for you.</p>"
